WEBVTT

00:00:01.117 --> 00:00:03.453 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Like many older ones before them,

00:00:03.453 --> 00:00:07.023 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
younger brothers and sisters
are taking on challenging assignments

00:00:07.023 --> 00:00:10.126 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that bring them rich spiritual rewards.

00:00:10.126 --> 00:00:14.898 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We go next to India to hear
from Brother Francis Rodrigues.

00:00:14.898 --> 00:00:18.568 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He’s using his training
from the School for Kingdom Evangelizers

00:00:18.568 --> 00:00:22.172 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to teach people
in the Indian Sign Language field.

00:03:54.951 --> 00:03:59.088 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Brother Rodrigues searches for those
rightly disposed for everlasting life

00:03:59.088 --> 00:04:02.825 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
wherever he can find them
despite the obstacles.

00:04:02.825 --> 00:04:06.562 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And you may have noted
that his joy comes from directing people

00:04:06.562 --> 00:04:10.633 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to the congregation to be part
of our true spiritual brotherhood.

00:04:10.633 --> 00:04:15.204 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That example is repeated millions
of times over through the diligent efforts

00:04:15.204 --> 00:04:18.908 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of publishers and pioneers
around the world.

00:04:18.908 --> 00:04:22.445 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Why not examine your ministry
to find ways to help

00:04:22.445 --> 00:04:25.715 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
yet more people to build
a good relationship with Jehovah?

